RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT B.BORROWER_REF_NO,B.BRANCH,B.DEPARTMENT_CODE,B.TREASURY_SOURCE,C.COUNTERPARTY,SUBSTR(O.SHORT_NAME,1,200) AS COUNTERPARTY_NAME ,C.USER_REF_NO,DECODE(P.TRANSACTIONPROCESS_STATUS,'P','PROCESSED','U','UNPROCESSED','W','WORK IN PROGRESS','F','FAILED','NON JOB PROCESSED') AS TRANSACTIONPROCESS_STATUS FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT C,LBVWS_BORR_TRNSPROC_STATUS B,LBTBS_BORR_PROC_STAT P,OLTMS_CUSTOMER O WHERE C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.BORROWER_REF_NO AND P.BORROWER_REF_NO = B.BORROWER_REF_NO AND O.CUSTOMER_NO=C.COUNTERPARTY
